<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Regulasi Keuangan - KPU Kabupaten Tabalong</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lucide/0.263.0/lucide.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        .tabalong-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e40af 100%);
        }
        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .card-hover:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
        }
        .glass-effect {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">

    <!-- Navigasi -->
    <nav class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-20 items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="bg-amber-500 p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-amber-200">
                        <i data-lucide="landmark" class="text-white w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="font-bold text-lg block leading-none text-slate-900 uppercase">KPU Tabalong</span>
                        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 font-semibold">Keuangan & Umum</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden lg:flex space-x-6 text-sm font-semibold">
                    <a href="#perpajakan" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition">Pajak</a>
                    <a href="#anggaran" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition">APBN/D</a>
                    <a href="#hibah" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition">Hibah</a>
                    <a href="#perbendaharaan" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition">Perbendaharaan</a>
                    <a href="#akuntansi" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition">Akuntansi</a>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <button class="hidden sm:block text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition text-sm font-bold">JDH KPU</button>
                    <button class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-200">
                        Login
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="tabalong-gradient text-white py-24 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0">
            <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-blue-200 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 border border-white/10">
                <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Kabupaten Tabalong
            </span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight">Pusat Regulasi <br><span class="text-amber-400">Keuangan Negara</span></h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Platform konsolidasi aturan hukum pengelolaan keuangan bagi Satker KPU Kabupaten Tabalong guna mewujudkan tata kelola pemilu yang transparan dan akuntabel.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="#pencarian" class="bg-white text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold hover:bg-slate-100 transition flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="search" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Cari Aturan
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold hover:bg-white/20 transition">
                    Unduh E-Book Regulasi
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Stat Ringkas -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 -mt-10 relative z-20">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-red-100 text-red-600 rounded-xl"><i data-lucide="file-text" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
            <div><span class="block text-2xl font-bold">120+</span><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase font-semibold">Produk Hukum</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-xl"><i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
            <div><span class="block text-2xl font-bold">2026</span><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase font-semibold">Update Terbaru</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-green-100 text-green-600 rounded-xl"><i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
            <div><span class="block text-2xl font-bold">Valid</span><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase font-semibold">Status Hukum</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 rounded-xl"><i data-lucide="download" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
            <div><span class="block text-2xl font-bold">98%</span><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase font-semibold">Tingkat Akses</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Kategori Regulasi Utama</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Pilih kategori untuk melihat daftar aturan hukum terkait pengelolaan dana pemilu.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <!-- Pajak -->
            <section id="perpajakan" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-slate-200 card-hover flex flex-col">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 mb-8">
                    <i data-lucide="receipt-text" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Pajak Negara</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Ketentuan pemotongan/pemungutan PPh dan PPN bagi instansi pemerintah serta kewajiban perpajakan badan adhoc (PPK/PPS/KPPS).</p>
                <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-red-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500 block mb-1">PMK 59/2022</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Pajak Instansi Pemerintah</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-red-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500 block mb-1">PP 94/2010</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Penghitungan Pajak Hibah</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-red-600 text-white font-bold hover:bg-red-700 transition">Buka Portal Pajak</button>
            </section>

            <!-- APBN & APBD -->
            <section id="anggaran" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-slate-200 card-hover flex flex-col">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mb-8">
                    <i data-lucide="landmark" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">APBN & APBD</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Landasan hukum pengelolaan APBN untuk operasional KPU dan APBD (melalui NPHD) untuk penyelenggaraan Pilkada Tabalong.</p>
                <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-blue-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-500 block mb-1">UU 17/2003</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Pokok Keuangan Negara</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-blue-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-500 block mb-1">PP 12/2019</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Pengelolaan Dana Daerah</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Detail Anggaran</button>
            </section>

            <!-- Hibah -->
            <section id="hibah" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-slate-200 card-hover flex flex-col">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600 mb-8">
                    <i data-lucide="hand-coins" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Regulasi Hibah</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Prosedur pengelolaan Naskah Perjanjian Hibah Daerah (NPHD), pendaftaran hibah ke DJPPR, dan pelaporannya.</p>
                <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-emerald-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-500 block mb-1">Permendagri 54/2019</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Pendanaan Pilkada</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-emerald-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-500 block mb-1">PKPU 13/2023</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Pedoman Pelaksanaan Hibah</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-600 text-white font-bold hover:bg-emerald-700 transition">Arsip NPHD</button>
            </section>

            <!-- Perbendaharaan -->
            <section id="perbendaharaan" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-slate-200 lg:col-span-2 card-hover">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10">
                    <div class="md:w-2/5">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 mb-8">
                            <i data-lucide="briefcase" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Perbendaharaan</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Pedoman teknis bagi Bendahara Pengeluaran (BPP) dalam penatausahaan uang persediaan, pembayaran langsung (LS), dan pengelolaan rekening.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl border border-amber-100 inline-flex">
                            <i data-lucide="info" class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-600"></i>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-800">Implementasi Aplikasi SAKTI 2024</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-3/5 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="border border-slate-100 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50/50">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">UU 1/2004</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Dasar utama Perbendaharaan Negara Indonesia.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border border-slate-100 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50/50">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">PMK 190/2012</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Tata cara pelaksanaan APBN di Satker.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border border-slate-100 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50/50">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">PMK 210/2022</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Standar Biaya Masukan (SBM) Terbaru.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border border-slate-100 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50/50">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">Pedoman KPU</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Keputusan KPU No. 64 Tahun 2024.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Akuntansi -->
            <section id="akuntansi" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-slate-200 card-hover flex flex-col">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 mb-8">
                    <i data-lucide="pie-chart" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Akuntansi Pemerintahan</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Standar Akuntansi Pemerintahan (SAP) berbasis akrual untuk penyusunan LRA, Neraca, dan Catatan atas Laporan Keuangan (CaLK).</p>
                <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-indigo-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-500 block mb-1">PP 71/2010</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Standar Akuntansi Pemerintah</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-white hover:border-indigo-200 transition">
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-500 block mb-1">PMK 225/2019</span>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Kebijakan Akuntansi Pemerintah Pusat</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-600 text-white font-bold hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">Format Laporan</button>
            </section>

        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Tabalong Section -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">
        <div class="tabalong-gradient rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-20 text-white relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
                <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                    <path d="M0 100 Q 50 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" />
                    <path d="M0 80 Q 50 -20 100 80" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Mewujudkan "Saraba Kawa" Melalui Transparansi</h2>
                <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed italic">
                    "Semangat kemandirian dan kerja keras Kabupaten Tabalong tercermin dalam setiap rupiah anggaran negara yang kami pertanggungjawabkan."
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
                        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold">WTP</span>
                        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-300">Opini BPK</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
                        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold">100%</span>
                        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-300">Penyaluran Adhoc</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full glass-effect rounded-[2rem] p-8">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-6">Informasi Kontak</h4>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-xl"><i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
                        <p class="text-sm">Jl. Tanjung Selatan No. 01 RT. VII Kelurahan Pembataan Kec. Murung Pudak, Kab. Tabalong, Kalsel.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-xl"><i data-lucide="phone" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
                        <p class="text-sm">(0526) 2023168 / kputabalong@gmail.com</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-xl"><i data-lucide="globe" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
                        <p class="text-sm">kab-tabalong.kpu.go.id</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white py-16 border-t border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-8">
                <div class="bg-slate-100 p-2 rounded-xl text-slate-700">
                    <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter">FINANCE<span class="text-blue-600">HUB</span> TABALONG</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm max-w-md mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Portal regulasi internal KPU Tabalong. Seluruh dokumen hukum di situs ini adalah salinan resmi untuk kepentingan edukasi dan operasional.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-12">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Twitter</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">YouTube</a>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-50 text-slate-400 text-xs">
                &copy; 2024 KPU Kabupaten Tabalong. Dikembangkan oleh Sub Bagian Keuangan, Umum, dan Logistik.
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Inisialisasi Ikon Lucide
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
